The paper deals with the optimization of a bidding strategy in the context of real-time ad auctions, which involves decision-making under uncertainty and the need to balance exploration and exploitation. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including game theory (cs.GT), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
